Create new project:

ng new <project-name> --style <css preprocessor> --routing

Run project:

ng serve --port <port>
         --host <localhost>
         --open open default browser
         --hmr anable hot model replacment
         --aot build using Ahead of Time compilation
         --base-href base url for the application being built

Lint project:

ng lint --fix fixes linting errors (may overwrite linted files)
        --type-check controls the type check for linting
        --force succeeds even if there was linting errors
        --silent show output text
        --format output format (prose, json, stylish, verbose, pmd, msbuild, checkstyle, vso, fileslist, codeFrame)

Unit test:

ng test --prod flag to set configuration to "prod"
        --environment defines the build environment
        --progress log progress to the console while building
        --watch run build when files change
        --code-coverage output a code coverage report

Generate files:
  --dry-run(-d) run through without making any changes
  --force(-f) forces overwriting of files

* Class
  ng g class <name> --spec specifies if a spec file is generated
                    --type specifies the type of class

* Component
  ng g component <name> --inline-style(-s) specifies if the style will be in the ts file
                        --inline-template(-t) specifies if the template will be in the ts file
                        --view-encapsulation(-v) specifies the view encapsulation strategy (None, Emulated, Native)
                        --change-detection(-c) specifies the change detection strategy (OnPush)
                        --styleext the file extension to be used for style files
                        --spec specifies if a spec file is generated
                        --flat flag to indicate if a dir is created
                        --module allows specification of the declaring module
                        --export specifies if declaring module exports the component

* Directive
  ng g directive <name> --spec specifies if a spec file is generated
                        --flat flag to indicate if a dir is created
                        --module allows specification of the declaring module
                        --export specifies if declaring module exports the component

* Enum
  ng g enum <name>

* Guard
  ng g guard <name> --spec specifies if a spec file is generated

* Enum
  ng g interface <name>

* Module
  ng g module <name> --routing generates a routing module
                     --routing-scope the scope for the generated routing (Root, Child)
                     --spec specifies if a spec file is generated
                     --flat flag to indicate if a dir is created

* Pipe
  ng g pipe <name> --spec specifies if a spec file is generated
                   --flat flag to indicate if a dir is created

* Service
  ng g service <name> --spec specifies if a spec file is generated
                      --flat flag to indicate if a dir is created

Build project:

ng build --prod flag to set configuration to "prod"
         --aot build using Ahead of Time compilation
